## Prioritize What Matters Most

Protected users receive full detection, remediation, and reporting coverage. At the same time, the system continues to monitor unprotected users, helping teams identify risk early and expand coverage in a controlled way.

This approach allows organizations to improve security coverage over time without overwhelming administrators.

